NOTE Language: en

00:00:04.456 --> 00:00:09.210
1996-0727 Evening Program At Guru Puja
Part 1, Cabella, Italy

01:20:43.576 --> 01:20:49.548
Hallo. Me and My family all visited Rome

01:20:49.749 --> 01:20:54.688
and saw the school and the children.

01:20:55.593 --> 01:21:03.632
It was really very sweet and very loving
expression

01:21:03.833 --> 01:21:06.939
of their joy that we saw there.

01:21:07.140 --> 01:21:11.937
And Mr. Shrivastava was very much
impressed by that,

01:21:12.138 --> 01:21:18.333
and he has given 11 million Italian Liras

01:21:18.534 --> 01:21:23.834
for the “Association of Culturale
Sahaja Yoga”.

01:22:08.746 --> 01:22:11.520
Guido: I mean,

01:22:13.109 --> 01:22:19.995
one feels really speechless in an occasion
like this.

01:22:20.196 --> 01:22:25.208
And I must say already Shri Mataji has been
so generous.

01:22:25.409 --> 01:22:30.659
And just imagine, last month She has
donated a brand new car,

01:22:30.860 --> 01:22:34.263
a Fiat called Brava, is a new model,

01:22:34.464 --> 01:22:39.921
fully equipped with air conditioning
and all the gadgets.

01:22:40.122 --> 01:22:44.100
And already we didn’t know what
to say, I mean,

01:22:44.301 --> 01:22:49.955
such a generosity is, of course, always
an example for all of us,

01:22:50.156 --> 01:22:55.301
and there is nothing we can do
to compare it. And...

01:22:55.502 --> 01:22:59.101
So, just from the bottom of our hearts,
we can only say:

01:22:59.302 --> 01:23:06.064
Thank You, Shri Mataji. Thank you, Sir C.P.
And what else?

01:23:06.265 --> 01:23:10.983
I’m running out of words!
